export const homeObjOne = {
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: "Immigrations Documents",
  headline: "Certified Translation Services",
  description:
    "Certified translations are for official uses where your receiver requires certification to verify that the translation is complete and accurate. This type of translation is commonly required for immigrations purposes. We translate all types of immigration documents like Visa, Iqama etc.",
  buttonLabel: "Get Started",
  imgStart: "",
  img: require("../../images/svg-1.svg"),
  alt: "Credit Card"
};

export const homeObjTwo = {
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: "Document Translation",
  headline: "Certified Document Translation",
  description:
    "We translate all types of documents like Employment contracts, labour contracts, business deals and agreements",
  buttonLabel: "Learn More",
  imgStart: "",
  img: require("../../images/svg-1.svg"),
  alt: "Vault"
};

export const homeObjThree = {
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: "Website Translation",
  headline: "Bilingual Websites",
  description:
    "If you are looking for an Arabic version for your business website, we can help you.  The website is the first thing customers think of when exploring a businesses. However, if your business is in the Middle East, then chances are that the majority of the population will speak only Arabic. We help you to develop an Arabic version for the existing webiste of your business or create a website both in English and Arabic.",
  buttonLabel: "Start Now",
  imgStart: "start",
  img: require("../../images/svg-1.svg"),
  alt: "Vault"
};
